  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ideal Nightmare</strong> is a tactical light/sound-based stealth game which features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Customizable weapons</strong> to fit your playstyle <br></li><li><strong>Explore various locales</strong> in an alternative WW1 history, where London has been taken over by blood cultists<br></li><li>Know if an enemy is nearby by the <strong>sound of their footsteps and breathing </strong><br></li><li><strong>Tension</strong> between lighting your way and not giving out your position</li></ul>",
